  "detailed_description": "Deathroids is a vertical scrolling shoot 'em up with amazing gameplay experience. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389010/extras/c338e50f683f7bf5bd02c3870b82be62.poster.avif?t=1751044108\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389010/extras/c338e50f683f7bf5bd02c3870b82be62.webm?t=1751044108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389010/extras/c338e50f683f7bf5bd02c3870b82be62.mp4?t=1751044108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>With a sci-fi theme, the game takes place in the distant future where a horde of alien robots are on their way to destroy planet Earth and you need to pilot the B.L.I.T. Battle Laser Interception Transport to stop them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389010/extras/93e80a3e0f576239d39f3b2af3dd9f5b.poster.avif?t=1751044108\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389010/extras/93e80a3e0f576239d39f3b2af3dd9f5b.webm?t=1751044108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389010/extras/93e80a3e0f576239d39f3b2af3dd9f5b.mp4?t=1751044108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The game has simple mechanics, where the player must pass through several waves of enemies without touching them and without being shot obviously, because there is no life bar. 80's arcade style, the game has a good variety of enemies, consequently challenges of pure skill.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389010/extras/80776dd43b3e762828ea57b7896a7b5d.poster.avif?t=1751044108\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389010/extras/80776dd43b3e762828ea57b7896a7b5d.webm?t=1751044108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389010/extras/80776dd43b3e762828ea57b7896a7b5d.mp4?t=1751044108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>With a soundtrack produced exclusively for the game, Deathroids has all the elements for good fun.",
  "about_the_game": "Deathroids is a vertical scrolling shoot 'em up with amazing gameplay experience. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389010/extras/c338e50f683f7bf5bd02c3870b82be62.poster.avif?t=1751044108\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389010/extras/c338e50f683f7bf5bd02c3870b82be62.webm?t=1751044108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389010/extras/c338e50f683f7bf5bd02c3870b82be62.mp4?t=1751044108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>With a sci-fi theme, the game takes place in the distant future where a horde of alien robots are on their way to destroy planet Earth and you need to pilot the B.L.I.T. Battle Laser Interception Transport to stop them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389010/extras/93e80a3e0f576239d39f3b2af3dd9f5b.poster.avif?t=1751044108\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389010/extras/93e80a3e0f576239d39f3b2af3dd9f5b.webm?t=1751044108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389010/extras/93e80a3e0f576239d39f3b2af3dd9f5b.mp4?t=1751044108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The game has simple mechanics, where the player must pass through several waves of enemies without touching them and without being shot obviously, because there is no life bar. 80's arcade style, the game has a good variety of enemies, consequently challenges of pure skill.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389010/extras/80776dd43b3e762828ea57b7896a7b5d.poster.avif?t=1751044108\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389010/extras/80776dd43b3e762828ea57b7896a7b5d.webm?t=1751044108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389010/extras/80776dd43b3e762828ea57b7896a7b5d.mp4?t=1751044108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>With a soundtrack produced exclusively for the game, Deathroids has all the elements for good fun.",
